Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The TWA Flight 800 crash
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjvnl
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 26 Jul 1996
The TWA Flight 800 crash and the media coverage of the accident, the casino life of the financial markets and Bob Dole's reluctance to embrace the 1990s.